      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To repeal certain tax subsidies enacted by the Energy Policy Act of 2005 for oil and gas, to allow a credit against income tax for farm diesel expenses, and to allow a credit to farmers who produce biodiesel and agri-biodiesel.</title>
